Note on data and assets:

The MIT license above applies to the source code in this repository. The
synthetic demonstration records, processed public sample JSON files and figure
image assets are provided for method demonstration only and must not be
redistributed or interpreted as a real-world pavement dataset. Raw point
clouds, full-route survey data and trained model weights are not included and
remain subject to institutional data-sharing restrictions.
